 of the primes: 2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13, or 17. For digit sum 2, there are 2 numbers (11 and 20). For digit sum 3, there are 3 numbers (12, 21, 30). For digit sum 5, I'm listing out the pairs where the digits add to 5.\n\nContinuing with digit sum 5, I have 5 numbers total (14, 23, 32, 41, 50). For digit sum 7, there are 7 numbers (16, 25, 34, 43, 52, 61, 70). For digit sum 11, I'm finding all two-digit numbers where the digits sum to 11, which gives me 8 numbers (29, 38, 47, 56, 65, 74, 83, 92). Now moving to digit sum 13, where I need a+b=13 with a between 4 and 9.\n\nFor digit sum 13, I have 6 numbers (49, 58, 67, 76, 85, 94). For digit sum 17, only 89 and 98 work, giving me 2 numbers. Adding up all the two-digit counts: 2 + 3 + 5 + 7 + 8 + 6 + 2 = 33. So the grand total is 4 one-digit numbers plus 33 two-digit numbers, which equals 37.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12312,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":12312},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c941b968-5a54-4dd9-b54c-7f2c212dde75","uuid":"981ce1bd-cd82-427c-ac2e-f03209a87efe"},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Y3c1TxGtj4JgSy29Ka1gct","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"37\n\n**Однозначные числа (1–9):** простая сумма цифр — это само число. Простые среди них: 2, 3, 5, 7 → **4 числа**.\n\n**Число 100:** сумма цифр = 1, не простое → **0**.\n\n**Двузначные числа (10–99):** для числа с цифрами *a* (десятки) и *b* (единицы) сумма цифр = a+b. Максимум 9+9=18. Простые в диапазоне 2–18: **2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13, 17**.\n\n| Сумма цифр | Пары (a, b) | Количество |\n|---|---|---|\n| 2 | 11, 20 | 2 |\n| 3 | 12, 21, 30 | 3 |\n| 5 | 14, 23, 32, 41, 50 | 5 |\n| 7 | 16, 25, 34, 43, 52, 61, 70 | 7 |\n| 11 | 29, 38, 47, 56, 65, 74, 83, 92 | 8 |\n| 13 | 49, 58, 67, 76, 85, 94 | 6 |\n| 17 | 89, 98 | 2 |\n\nДвузначных: 2+3+5+7+8+6+2 = **33**.\n\nЗакономерность простая — для суммы *s* количество двузначных чисел с a+b=s равно min(s, 10) − max(s−9, 1) + 1. Суммы 4, 6, 8, 9, 10, 12, 14, 15, 16, 18 — составные, их пропускаем.\n\n**Итого: 4 + 33 = 37.**"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12312,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":12312},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c941b968-5a54-4dd9-b54c-7f2c212dde75","uuid":"3295e349-9203-4712-a07b-6a6c6ed57cb7"},{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":24344,"duration_api_ms":27497,"num_turns":1,"result":"37\n\n**Однозначные числа (1–9):** простая сумма цифр — это само число. Простые среди них: 2, 3, 5, 7 → **4 числа**.\n\n**Число 100:** сумма цифр = 1, не простое → **0**.\n\n**Двузначные числа (10–99):** для числа с цифрами *a* (десятки) и *b* (единицы) сумма цифр = a+b. Максимум 9+9=18. Простые в диапазоне 2–18: **2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13, 17**.\n\n| Сумма цифр | Пары (a, b) | Количество |\n|---|---|---|\n| 2 | 11, 20 | 2 |\n| 3 | 12, 21, 30 | 3 |\n| 5 | 14, 23, 32, 41, 50 | 5 |\n| 7 | 16, 25, 34, 43, 52, 61, 70 | 7 |\n| 11 | 29, 38, 47, 56, 65, 74, 83, 92 | 8 |\n| 13 | 49, 58, 67, 76, 85, 94 | 6 |\n| 17 | 89, 98 | 2 |\n\nДвузначных: 2+3+5+7+8+6+2 = **33**.\n\nЗакономерность простая — для суммы *s* количество двузначных чисел с a+b=s равно min(s, 10) − max(s−9, 1) + 1. Суммы 4, 6, 8, 9, 10, 12, 14, 15, 16, 18 — составные, их пропускаем.\n\n**Итого: 4 + 33 = 37.**","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"c941b968-5a54-4dd9-b54c-7f2c212dde75","total_cost_usd":0.12001,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tok